Installation from source package
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

FreePascal compiler is required to compile the program. On DOS and Windows
operating systems, FreePascal's BIN directory contains the compiler and
additional necessary utilities (make, rstconv), so this directory must be
included in the PATH.

1. On Unix-like systems
-----------------------

  Build:      $ ./configure
              $ make
  Install:    # sudo make install
  Remove:     # make uninstall

2. On Windows
~~~~~~~~~~~~~

  Build:      > cd source
              > make -f Makefile.w??

3. On DOS
~~~~~~~~~

  Build:      > cd source
              > make -f Makefile.dos

